se is\nnot displayed by the model where the rewiring occurs only to voters sharing the\nsame opinion, studied by other authors. Our results are backed up by Monte\nCarlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Apr 2020 18:14:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 14:00:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 07:54:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-02"}
