ata Fusion Contest Dataset by comparing with other\nprevalent point cloud deep learning models demonstrate the favorable\ngeneralization capability of the proposed model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 05:12:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-21"}
