ee. The main technical contribution is\ncontrolling what marginal distributions and derivatives are achievable and\nusing Cauchy's functional equation to argue existence of the gadgets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 12:41:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 16:42:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Jul 2021 11:12:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-20"}
